<placeName cert="high">?</placeName></head><div lang="grc" part="N" type="edition"><ab part="N">
    <lb n="1"/>Ἀγαθὸς Δαίμων Κρονίωνι τῷ φιλτάτῳ χαίρειν. πρὸ μὲν 

    <lb n="2"/>πάντων τὸ προσκύνημά σου ποιῶ παρὰ τῷ κυρίῳ Σαράπι. γινώ-

    <lb n="3"/><choice><corr>σκειν</corr><sic>γεινωσκιν</sic></choice> σε θέλω ὅτι <choice><corr>οὐχ</corr><sic>ουκ</sic></choice> ὡς ἐγώ σοι ἐχρησάμην, καὶ σὺ ἐμοί. 

    <lb n="4"/>καὶ οὐ μόνον ἀλλὰ καὶ ἄντικρυς τοῦ <choice><corr>θείου</corr><sic>θεου</sic></choice> <choice><corr>Εὐσταθίου</corr><sic>ευσταθις</sic></choice> οὐκ ἔ-

    <lb n="5"/>γραψάς μοι καθὼς σὺ εἶπας, ἀλλ᾽ ἐγώ σοι ἤδη δευτέραν 

    <lb n="6"/>ἐπιστολήν σοι πέμπω, ὥστε οὖν μὴ ἀμελήσῃς 

    <lb n="7"/>τοῦ μοι γράψαι ἐπιστολὴν περὶ τῶν γεινομένων. 

    <lb n="8"/>ἀσπάζου τὴν μητέρα σου καὶ τούς σου πάντας. 

    <lb n="9"/>ἐρρῶσθαί σε εὔχομαι πανοικεὶ βούλομαι. </ab></div><div n="meta.27068" part="N" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.27068" part="N" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notAfter="200" notBefore="101" type="textDate">II</date></p></div><div n="meta.27068" part="N" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl><bibl subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Bon.</title><biblScope type="numbers">44</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">27068</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP"><series>0081</series>; ; <biblScope type="numbers">44</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0081;;44" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.27068" part="N" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p>keine</p></div><div n="meta.27068" part="N" subtype="otherPublications" type="bibliography"><head>Andere Publikation</head><bibl subtype="other" type="publication">SB V 7616</bibl></div><div n="meta.27068" part="N" subtype="locations" type="history"><p><placeName cert="low" type="ancientFindspot">Tebtynis (Arsinoites)</placeName></p></div><div n="meta.27068" part="N" type="figure"><p><figure href="http://www.librit.unibo.it/servlet/ParseHtml/page/frames/index.html?idimmagine=&amp;idoggetto=119"><figDesc>Abbildung im Internet</figDesc></figure></p></div></body></text></TEI.2>